Hi Mel! Beautiful Paris 😍 awesome Vlog! Just one thing I wanna mention, my personal thoughts and you know I'm a fan of yours so...I'm just saying it as I would to a friend of mine ☺️
And that's about luxury goods using animal skin 🙁 like that lady was describing the bag lined with goat skin...I was really taken aback...you know I appreciate all the craftsmanship that goes into making delicate items, and that's artistry to me...BUT the material...I mean...I don't think our love of luxury goodies is worth the brutality on animals 🙁
I think you have a good heart and you don't mean to be insensitive at all...I'm just saying maybe we should think again about items that are made up of animals
